Strategy Overview:

Uses FALN (iShares Fallen Angels USD Bond ETF) as the main instrument
Compares it against HYG (High Yield) and LQD (Investment Grade) ETFs
Implements a spread-based trading strategy

Key Components:
Spread calculation between Fallen Angels and High Yield bonds
Z-score based signal generation
Long-short portfolio construction
Comprehensive performance metrics

Features:
Historical data fetching using yfinance
Spread analysis and signal generation
Performance metrics calculation (Sharpe, Sortino, Drawdown)
Visualization of results with three plots:
Cumulative returns
Spread and trading signals
Rolling Sharpe ratio
